OL,5, A review of the clinical records of 44 
OL,6, patients who died under the care of    
OL,7, former neurologist Michael Watt has    
OL,8, found "significant failures in their   
OL,9, treatment" and "poor communication with
OL,10, families".                             
OL,12,FWhile this review looked at a sample of
OL,13,F44 deceased cases potentially thousands
OL,14,Fmore could be affected.                
OL,16,FThe review arises from a 2018 recall of
OL,17,F2,500 outpatients who were in Dr Watt's
OL,18,Fcare at the Belfast Health Trust.      
OL,20,FHe worked there until 2017.            
